sql: SELECT SUM(lo_revenue) AS lo_revenue, d_year, p_brand FROM ssb.p_lineorder LEFT JOIN ssb.dates ON lo_orderdate = d_datekey LEFT JOIN ssb.part ON lo_partkey = p_partkey LEFT JOIN ssb.supplier ON lo_suppkey = s_suppkey WHERE p_brand BETWEEN 'MFGR#0201' AND 'MFGR#0208' AND s_region = 'ASIA' GROUP BY d_year, p_brand ORDER BY d_year, p_brand
